  "title": "Super Hot",
  "description": "Makes your torch SUPERHOT",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Made for <a href=\"https://github.com/MinecraftModDevelopment/MMD-Site/blob/master/docs/events/spooky_jam_2019.md\">MMD Spookyjam 2019</a>.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">In this mod, the torch is literally untouchable.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> If you strike somebody with a torch then it burns!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Even the TNT is scared and explodes if you dismantle it with a torch!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">It's a realistic feature, it always annoyed me that it never worked. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Now it's working!</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 24px; color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Features:</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">-<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">TNT</span> </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">explodes when you break it down (with a torch) (1.1+)</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">-If you attack with a torch, it <strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">burns</span></strong>! (1.0+)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">-<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">All Torch Mods are Compatible</span><strong>! </strong>(1.1+)</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Discord for Mods (DE):&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/wX9hAud\">Klick</a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Discord for Mods (ENG): <a href=\"https://discord.gg/e9dJer8\">Klick</a></span></p>",
